The series[i]-graph.data[i].category should be the index of certain category in categories.

So the code should be:
```
data: [
                {
                  draggable: true,
                  name: "AGOTOZ",
                  symbolSize: 120
                },
                {
                  name: "节点1",//  节点名称
                  category: 0,
                  symbolSize: 60// 标签大小
                },
                {
                  name: "节点2",//  节点名称
                  category: 1,
                  symbolSize: 90// 标签大小
                }
],// 数据渲染

```

